description: Archer has been staying at Tanner's house for a minute. Archer has a huge crush on Tanner but Tanner is straight, but, oh, so hot! So, of course, a gay dude has to do what a gay dude has to do---try to seduce their straight friend. At least once, every dude should experiment. So Tanner was showering and Archer walked in and began his seduction. These two teen boys are banging. Banging!
title: Handle Me
